Developed an interactive Power BI Contact Center Performance Dashboard to monitor and analyze operational KPIs such as call volume, SLA, PCA, AHT, abandoned calls, and agent performance. The dashboard provides a centralized view of contact center operations, enabling stakeholders to track productivity, service quality, and customer experience effectively.

The report includes multiple analytical pages with dynamic filters, KPI tracking, and trend analysis for better operational decision-making.

🎯 Objective
To monitor contact center operational performance
To analyze inbound call trends and service levels
To track agent and queue-wise performance metrics
To improve decision-making through interactive reporting

